creator: Aline Kilmer
description:
LibriVox recording of An Autumn Walk with Deborah by Aline Kilmer.

Read in English by Ian King; Jason Mills; Lee Ann Howlett; Larry Greene; Leonard Wilson; MaryAnn Spiegel; Marina Tsung; and Rosslyn Carlyle.

Librivox volunteers bring you eight readings of An Autumn Walk with Deborah by Aline Kilmer. This was the weekly poetry project for the week of October 12, 2014.

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (5MB)
